node.text:
It all started with an idea.

I’ve always wanted to host an event but I wanted to incorporate the things that have made me most successful such as breath work, meditation, yoga and my morning routine; rather than having a big stage, guest speakers and sales pitches.

I wasn’t sure how I was to facilitate everything on my own so, my idea never manifested until I planted that seed inside my partner @onyay after having experienced one of her life changing breath work journeys in Tulum.

After connecting with Onyay and sharing my plans over dinner, I came to learn that she had been looking for someone to collaborate with too. We decided to come together to form our own retreat company: @empowered_retreats Retreats.

With Onyay’s 20 years of experience in breath work facilitation and my experience in entrepreneurship we combined forces to intertwine the 2 worlds: spirituality and business.

This video showcases our first retreat in Tulum where we had the honor of connecting, facilitating and exploring with 11 beautiful souls.

Thank you so much to @noemi__hopper @kimyurcisin @onyay @dylan.kreiser @mr_dawkins_ @erikjasperkier @cathy.tayag.kier @zeke.pike @andreannavanquelef @garthtubbs for coming!

Special thanks to @ahoritafilms for capturing everything so beautifully.

Where should we host our 2nd Retreat in June?

#tulum #tulummexico #retreat #empoweredretreats #empower #travel

It all starts with YOU.

By creating a better life for yourself, you will spread positivity, love and abundance to everyone around you.

All you need is an hour to yourself every morning.

No outside distractions.

A notebook.

A pen.

Hydrate,

Stretch,

Write down 10 things your grateful for,

Write a love letter to money,

Write down 5 things you can take action on TODAY that will get you one step closer to your goal,

Meditate for 10 minutes or more,

Say 10 OUT LOUD affirmations,

And spread this movement by posting a picture of your morning routine with #MRM and tagging @colinyurcisin

If this changed my life, there’s no reason it can’t change yours!

 THE GOAL IS TO HAVE:

1 MILLION PEOPLE JOIN #MRM

TO JOIN THE “#MRM”...

(1) LIKE THIS PICTURE✅

(2) FOLLOW ME, @colinyurcisin✅

(3) TAG 3 FRIENDS BELOW AND SAY “IM IN”✅

(4) POST A STORY OF YOUR MRM NOTEBOOK, HASHTAG #MRM AND TAG @COLINYURCISIN✅

This will change millions of lives,

And it all starts with YOU.

#MRM #lifechanged #morningroutine #postivevibes #love #positivity #happy #changetheworld

node.text:
DM ME “MASTERCLASS” TO BE CONSIDERED FOR THE PROGRAM.
•
Masterclass has been created for action takers who are ready to take their understanding of credit to the next level.
•
I will be taking on 5 students who meet all of my requirements to repair, rebuild, and master their credit.
•
This class will not make you an overnight success.
•
This involves time, consistent action, and commitment.
•
The Masterclass will include:
1. A full credit sweep (If needed) - We will remove all negatives from your file.
2. Authorized users and primaries to age your file (If you do not need the credit sweep this will be included in the cost).
3. Lifetime access to @creditclass and the telegram community chat.
4. Coaching calls with me & access to my personal cell.
5. Lifetime access to my “Chosen Ones Mastermind” Facebook group where we have our recorded weekly live calls with top entrepreneurs around the world.
•
This mentorship is designed to not only recreate your credit file, but will also allow me to share my expertise with you so that you can learn and apply all of my methods yourself.
•
The Masterclass will change your entire outlook on what is possible with credit and will guide you to achieving all of your personal and business goals.
•
Please do not inquire about the program if you are not ready to make an investment in yourself and cannot commit to at least 3 months of learning and taking consistent action.
•
Let’s win.

This card is a MUST.

node.text:
I bought myself a present this weekend.

I’m coming up on my two year anniversary as an Entrepreneur.

It’s crazy to think that 2 summers ago I was driving around in my Volkswagen Passat in the 115° Arizona heat, knocking on hundreds of doors a day attempting to wholesale real estate.

I never closed 1 deal and I failed my first 3 businesses.

I was $50K in debt and less than 2 years later im buying Range Rovers for more than $50K+ in CASH.

The best part is…

I haven’t changed one bit.

I work just as hard as I did when I was driving a Volkswagen. 

And I’m just as happy and motivated as I was back then too.

The only thing that’s changed is the commas in my bank account and my Bitcoin wallet ;)

Life is a beautiful thing when you manifest everything from nothing but a little thought in your head.

I’m no different than you, I just work hard, stay focused and never give up.

What dream car are you going to manifest?

#rangerover #landrover #manifest #dreamcar #success #motivation #carsofig

Happy 1 year anniversary @noemihopperr 

I’m so happy and grateful the Universe brought you into my life back in Bali last year.

Still blows my mind how I barley caught you.

My first day there was your last day and to think you wouldn’t even give me your number (Just IG) is crazy🤣

Thank you Luigis pizza for making @noemihopperr crave a slice that day and giving us the best place to meet.

I knew the second I saw you I had to have you.

To think that I wouldn’t see you for another 6 months after that day is so crazy.

I’m so happy you trusted me and allowed me to fly you to Tulum later that summer.

I can say without a doubt that life has been 10X more fun, meaningful and exciting with you.

To many more adventures to come.

I love you.

#anniversary #ibiza #summer #success #freedom #girlfriendsofig

node.text:
Barcelona is special to me.

4 years ago I came here for the first time in a study abroad program with friends from college.

I was the first person in my entire family to get the chance to experience Europe.

I’ll never forget how excited I was getting on the plane at EWR looking at the flight map and seeing the destination on the other side of the Atlantic Ocean.

I was going into unchartered territory and I couldn’t be more excited.

That summer I spent 2 months roaming around Spain without a worry in the world.

I’ve never had so much fun and freedom in my life.

Towards the end of the trip the sadness set in because I knew that the life I was setting myself up for wouldn’t allow this type of freedom.

That was the first time in my life I became aware of how much money and time you really needed to truly be able to enjoy life.

I knew that my $38K salary a year paying job out of college was never going to get me this lifestyle.

Barcelona, 4 years ago is when my seed of entrepreneurship was planted.

I was a broke college kid with a new dream to become successful so I could do whatever I want and experience the best things life had to offer..

And 4 years later I’m finally back, except this time i don’t have to beg my Mom for an extra $100 a week🤣 (She’s happily retired by me too now btw).

A seed can be planted at any time.

All it takes is a little inspiration and a small thought that maybe one day your life can be exactly what you dreamed.

#success #entrepreneur #barcelona #spain #instatravel

node.text:
25 years on earth.

Loving every second of it.

I am grateful for @noemi__hopper , my family, my best friends and all of my supporters.

I’m even grateful for my haters!

I wouldn’t be here without your support and love.

My goal for 25 is to break an 8 figure net worth (the fact that this has a more than probable chance of happening is mind blowing to me), continue to educate and teach Bitcoin, build up my community on all of my social media platforms (omnipresence), launch @creditclass 2.0, continue to travel in luxury and abundance around the world, get a spot in Brickell, Miami, go on even more family vacations and impact millions of lives.

Every damn day I wake up full of excitement to do what I’m passionate about.

I always like to remind you that 2 years ago on this day I was working at a corporate job making $35K a year, $50K in debt with no direction in life.

All it takes is one decision, hard work, persistence and faith to change your life forever.

If I can do it then you can 100% do it.

Blessed for another day.

Cheers to 25.

I love you all.

#25 #birthday #bitcoin #success #travel

node.text:
It all started with an idea.

I’ve always wanted to host an event but I wanted to incorporate the things that have made me most successful such as breath work, meditation, yoga and my morning routine; rather than having a big stage, guest speakers and sales pitches.

I wasn’t sure how I was to facilitate everything on my own so, my idea never manifested until I planted that seed inside my partner @onyay after having experienced one of her life changing breath work journeys in Tulum.

After connecting with Onyay and sharing my plans over dinner, I came to learn that she had been looking for someone to collaborate with too. We decided to come together to form our own retreat company: @empowered_retreats Retreats.

With Onyay’s 20 years of experience in breath work facilitation and my experience in entrepreneurship we combined forces to intertwine the 2 worlds: spirituality and business.

This video showcases our first retreat in Tulum where we had the honor of connecting, facilitating and exploring with 11 beautiful souls.

Thank you so much to @noemi__hopper @kimyurcisin @onyay @dylan.kreiser @mr_dawkins_ @erikjasperkier @cathy.tayag.kier @zeke.pike @andreannavanquelef @garthtubbs for coming!

Special thanks to @ahoritafilms for capturing everything so beautifully.

Where should we host our 2nd Retreat in June?

#tulum #tulummexico #retreat #empoweredretreats #empower #travel
